==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
With reference to Genesis 2:17: ‘But of the tree of the knowledge of good and evil, thou shalt not eat of it: for in the day that thou eatest thereof thou shalt surely die.’ (KJV)

===Noun===
'''[[forbidden]] [[fruit]]'''
#the fruit forbidden to [[w:Adam|Adam]]
#illicit pleasure; something that one should not take or get involved with, such as an another person's [[spouse]]

